
Compile:
$ g++ -o ../diffusion_1D_multistate -O2 -std=c++11 diffusion_1D_multistate.cpp

--
Compile for debugging:
$ g++ -o ../diffusion_1D_multistate -ggdb -O2 -std=c++11 diffusion_1D_multistate.cpp

Run:
$ gdb ~/../diffusion_1D_multisurf
(gdb) run [input file]
(gdb) bt               <- back tracing
(gdb) q                <- quit
--

Compile error of 'nr3.h' with g++ 4.8:

In 'nr3mod.h', 'throw' keyword is replaced with 'NRthrow' to fix the error.

